==EACPT Congresses<ref>http://www.eacpt.org/?q=node/1</ref>==
Congresses<ref>http://www.eacpt.org/?q=node/1</ref> are open to delegates from Europe and anywhere in the world, including health professionals, researchers, biotechnology and pharmaceutical industry professionals, regulators, policy makers, ethicists and others interested in drug discovery, and in clinical, cost-effectiveness and safety of medicines and related biomarkers. 
